<paragraph id="7478F247F8D0C7BF3B321BFDEA222256" pageId="52" pageNumber="53">
GREECE, Parnassus, Lake Zouvala, 
<emphasis id="AFBA64A476F34423A6093A9A743C01B6" italics="true" pageId="52" pageNumber="53">R.Maire</emphasis>
